</section>

<section id="projects" class="projects-section py-5" style="background-color: #f4f1ee;">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5">Projects</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted mb-4">I'd love to hear from you — whether it's about a project, collaboration, or just to say hello.</p>
